":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34354,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/08\/04\/dua-nightmares\/","url_meta":{"origin":34814,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nightmares: Supplication upon being scared by a dream","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 4, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you is frightened by a dream during sleep, let him say: I seek refuge in the perfect words of Allah from His anger, His punishment, and the evil of His servants, from\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20051,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/11\/26\/dua-leaving-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":34814,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for leaving home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say when leaving the house, \u201cIn the name of Allah, I trust in Allah. O Allah, we seek refuge in You from misstepping or being led astray, from wronging or being wronged, from abusing or being abused.\" Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34814","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminae